title: Adorable Baby Possum Won't Let Go of Tiny Stuffed Kangaroo
text:
> Entertainment Adorable Baby Possum Won't Let Go of Tiny Stuffed Kangaroo An orphaned baby possum is refusing to let go of its favorite toy kangaroo as an Australian zoo nurses her back to health. Jen Markham (@jenmarkham) has the adorable video. The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
